# Security Policy

## Reporting a Vulnerability

We take the security of EliteFolks seriously. If you discover a security vulnerability, please do NOT open a public issue. This helps protect the community while we work on a fix.

### How to report:
Please send an email to **elitefolksteam@gmail.com**.

### What to include:
- A description of the vulnerability.
- Steps to reproduce the issue.
- Potential impact of the bug.

We will acknowledge your report within 48 hours and provide a timeline for a resolution. Thank you for keeping EliteFolks safe!
